the ATM machines. ATM machines should tell you their withdrawal limit, not how much is left. Also even more than that, when you try to withdraw 100 EUR (It's even possible to withdraw more here), the system tells you You can withdraw 100 EUR and 82 cents. Or instead of telling you the limit, they could at least show you how much You have left even after a withdrawal. That way You can see for yourself if there is enough money left for You have what You thought You need.

TL;DR

ATMs should say (in EU banknotes/pins) how purse business idea and guess what. 

Btw: ATM hasn't voted, it's fine as it is, but if it can be improved, lets improve it! :D
